        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Introduction to the Foundation Level Extensions",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "his overview document is intended for anyone with an interest in the ISTQB Foundation Level",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "xtensions who wants a high-level introduction to the leading principles and an overview of the individual",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "extension syllabi.",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "rom time to time, ISTQB will update this document to reflect any additional extensions that shall be",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "introduced for the Foundation Level, or to reflect major changes in existing ones. Publications of the",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "updated document will be available on the ISTQB website.",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "he ISTQB Foundation and Advanced Level syllabi have been defined and have been on the market for",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "some time. New topics emerge due to technology and methodology changes in the market which often",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "are brought into the ISTQB program as new Expert Level syllabi. However, not all topics are suited for the",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "xpert Level. For this reason, the extension syllabi are established at the Foundation Level to expand the",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "introduced by the ISTQB periodically. Extensions may be established at the Advanced Level as well, but",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "that is beyond the scope of this document.",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "he following Foundation Level Extension syllabus has been released:",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "gile Tester",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "n this document, each Foundation Level Extension syllabus is summarized and the associated Business",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "utcomes are stated. The Business Outcomes communicate what can be expected from a person who",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "achieves a Foundation Level Extension Certification in a particular subject area (e.g., Agile Tester), and",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "will outline the benefits for companies that are considering the development of specific testing skills at this",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "level.",
            "page": 6
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "ersion 2014",
            "page": 6
