            "level": "H3",
            "text": "verview",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Introduction to Foundation Level Agile Tester Extension",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "he certification for Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester is designed for professionals who are",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "working within Agile environments. It is also for professionals who are planning to start implementing",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "gile methods in the near future, or are working within companies that plan to do so, The certification",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "provides an advantage for those who would like to know the required Agile activities, roles, methods, and",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "methodologies specific to their role.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Intended Audience",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "he Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester qualification is aimed at four main groups of professionals:",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Professionals who have achieved in-depth testing experience in traditional methods and would",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "like to get an Agile Tester Certificate.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Junior professional testers who are just starting in the testing profession, have received the",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "oundation Level certificate, and would like to know more about the tester’s role in an Agile",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "environment.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Professionals who are relatively new to testing and are required to implement test approaches,",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "methods and techniques in their day to day job in Agile projects.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Professionals who are experienced in their role (including unit testing) and need more",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "understanding and knowledge about how to perform and manage testing on all levels in Agile",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "projects.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "hese professionals include people who are in roles such as testers, test analysts, test engineers, test",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "consultants, test managers, user acceptance testers, and software developers.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "his Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester certification may also be appropriate for anyone who",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "wants a deeper understanding of software testing in the Agile world, such as project managers, quality",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "managers, software development managers, business analysts, IT directors, and management",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "consultants.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Career Paths for Testers",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "uilding on the Foundation Level, the Agile Tester Extension supports the definition of career paths for",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "professional testers. A person with the Agile Tester certificate has extended the broad understanding of",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "testing acquired at the Foundation Level to enable him or her to work effectively as a professional tester in",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "an Agile project.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "eople possessing an ISTQB Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester certificate may use the Certified",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "ester Foundation Level acronym CTFL-AT.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Learning Objectives",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "n general, the Foundation Level syllabus is examinable at a K1 level, i.e., the candidate will recognize,",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "remember and recall terms and concepts stated in the Foundation Level syllabus.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "n addition, all Foundation Level syllabus learning objectives are examinable at the same K- level in an",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "extension exam.",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "ersion 2014",
            "page": 7
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "nternational",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "verview",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "hat said, each extension level exam focuses on the learning objectives defined in that extension",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "syllabus. The relevant learning objectives at K1, K2, and K3 levels are provided at the beginning of each",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "chapter within each particular extension syllabus.",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Entry Requirements",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "o be able to participate in a Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester exam, candidates must have",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "obtained the ISTQB Foundation Level certificate.",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Structure and Course Duration",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "he Foundation Level Extension – Agile Tester syllabus has no shared or common elements with the",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "oundation Level syllabus.",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "he syllabi must be taught in the following minimum number of days:",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "yllabus",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "ays",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "aseline: Foundation",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "xtension: Agile Tester",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "he following figure shows the structure of the Agile Tester Extension and its relationship to the",
            "page": 8
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "oundation Level.",
            "page": 8
        },
