            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "scenarios, requirements and acceptance criteria as appropriate.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "FM7",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "styles and channels.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "n general, a Certified Tester Foundation Level – Agile Tester is expected to have acquired the necessary",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "skills to working effectively within an Agile team and environment.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "Content",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "hapter 1: Agile Software Development",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "anifesto.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "early and frequent feedback.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "business representatives.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "improvement in Agile projects.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "adds value in each of these activities.",
            "page": 10
        },
        {
