        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "hapter 2: Fundamental Agile Testing Principles, Practices, and Processes",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "and non-Agile projects.",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H2",
            "text": "gile projects.",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "testing in an Agile project, including test progress and product quality.",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "explain why test automation is important to manage regression risk in Agile projects.",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H1",
            "text": "hapter 3: Agile Testing Methods, Techniques, and Tools",
            "page": 11
        },
        {
            "level": "H3",
            "text": "driven development, and behavior-driven development.",
            "page": 11
        },
